Circle - Class in <Unnamed>
the Circle class inherits from twoDimensionalShape and implements the TwoDimensionalShape interface.
Circle() - Constructor for class Circle
The blank circle constructor makes a unit circle with dimensions all equal to 1
Circle(double) - Constructor for class Circle
The circle constructor with 1 argument is used to create a circle object with the dimension1 set to the parameter.
Circle(double, double) - Constructor for class Circle
The circle constructor with 2 arguments is used to create a circle with dimensions set to the passed values.
